column2: SELECT TOP # s.z as redshift, s.subclass, s.elodieSpType as spectraltype, s.elodieBV as color, s.elodieTEff as temperature, s.elodieLogG as gravity, s.elodieFeH as metallicity, m.age, m.SFR FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort as m ON m.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE s.subClass ! = #
